Class DoubleHistogram

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.lmu.ifi.dbs.elki.utilities.datastructures.histogram.AbstractStaticHistogram

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Histogram
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DoubleDynamicHistogram

    public class DoubleHistogram
extends AbstractStaticHistogram
    Histogram class storing double values. The histogram will start with "bin" bins, but it can grow dynamically to the left and right.
    Since:
    0.5.5
    Author:
    Erich Schubert
